title: Customer support experience
text: Every single time there is something wrong. For example you have a missing item with Uber eats or you need a refund because your driver canceled. The customer service is literally impossible to get a hold of or find on the app in any shape or form. If you can get around without using Uber do it at all cost. Money hungry share holders trying to rake all profits in and not pay one mind to experience. Simply disgusting.

title: Amazingly bad customer service
text: Seems borderline criminal that a company this large doesn't have a usable customer service line. My Uber eats orders get lost or stolen about half the time and there's no recourse at all. Can't believe this company leveraged tax loopholes to a near monopoly despite a truly horrible product. What a shame.
